<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to UniNav!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333; /* --text-color-dark approximation */
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f0f8ff; /* --bg-main */
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
      color: #f0f8ff; /* --text-color-light-two */
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff; /* Lighter background for content */
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      border: 1px solid #ccebff; /* Lighter shade derived from --border-color */
      border-top: none;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280; /* --muted-foreground approximation */
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block; /* Changed from block for better flow if needed */
      background-color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
      color: #f0f8ff !important; /* --text-color-light-two, !important */
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 20px; /* Standardized padding */
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: none;
      text-align: center; /* Ensure text is centered */
    }
     .button:hover {
       background-color: #002a50; /* Slightly darker shade of --bg-dark for hover */
    }
    h1, h2, h3 { /* Apply primary color to headings */
      color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
    }
    .feature {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      border-left: 3px solid #75bfff; /* --bg-submain */
    }
    .next-steps {
      background-color: #e6f2ff; /* Lighter shade of --bg-main */
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    ul, ol {
      padding-left: 20px; /* Ensure lists have padding */
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    a { /* Standard link color */
        color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to UniNav!</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>!</p>

    <p>We're excited to welcome you to <strong>UniNav</strong> - your new hub for university study materials and academic resources!</p>

    <h2>About UniNav</h2>
    <p>UniNav is a collaborative platform where students can share, discover, and organize academic resources. You've joined the <%= departmentName %> department community!</p>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3>ðŸ“š What You Can Do:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Access course materials organized by faculty, department and level</li>
        <li>Upload and share your own study resources</li>
        <li>Bookmark materials and create personal collections</li>
        <li>Write blogs and earn from your academic insights</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="next-steps">
      <h3>ðŸš€ Next Steps:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Verify your email</strong> by clicking the verification link sent to your inbox (if not already done).</li>
        <li><strong>Complete your profile</strong> by adding your academic interests.</li>
        <li><strong>Explore materials</strong> in your department.</li>
        <li><strong>Upload your first study resource</strong> to help fellow students.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <a href="https://uninav.com/explore" class="button" style="color: #f0f8ff !important;">Start Exploring</a>

    <p>If you have any questions, check out our <a href="https://uninav.com/help" style="color: #003666;">Help Center</a> or contact our support team at <a href="mailto:uninav.buildminds@gmail.com" style="color: #003666;">uninav.buildminds@gmail.com</a>.</p>

    <p>Happy studying!</p>
    <p>The UniNav Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> UniNav. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>You're receiving this email because you signed up for UniNav.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
